---
alwaysApply: true
---

This repo contains both real domain logic and mock/demo layers.

When touching a feature, classify it first:
- canonical runtime domain logic
- local mock/demo screen
- adapter/seam between mock and real
- placeholder UI with no backend contract

Do not silently convert a mock/demo surface into a real integration.
Do not silently remove a demo fallback.
Do not infer canonical behavior from seed data, localStorage stubs, or placeholder tabs.

If a task introduces persistence into a mock area:
- make the seam explicit
- preserve current fallback behavior unless the request explicitly retires it
- note what remains mock and what became real
